units.description: New 2024 Forest River RV Cedar Creek Cottage 40CFD
units.details:
Forest River Cedar Creek Cottage destination trailer 40CFD highlights:

  • Covered Front Deck
  • Triple Entry Doors
  • Fireplace
  • King Bed Slide Out
  • Shower with a Seat
  • Two Power Awnings

 

If you need more sleeping or storage space, this destination trailer is the one for you! There is a front covered porch with sliding glass doors that enters in to the front living area. Here, you'll enjoy relaxing on the sectional hide-a-bed sofa across from the entertainment center and fireplace. The spacious bar top with two seats will provide a place to dine, and the middle kitchen is any chef's dream with its two pantries, spacious 20 cu. ft. 12V refrigerator, and plenty of counter space! When you're ready for your own space, you can retreat to the rear bedroom where you'll find a king bed slide out, a wardrobe, a dresser, drawers, and even washer and dryer prep. The comfort doesn't stop there! There is also a loft above the full bath that includes a ladder and a mattress, so you can use this space for more sleeping or storage space!

 

Each time you visit your favorite camping destination, you'll be so grateful to find the Forest River Cedar Creek Cottage destination trailer waiting for you! The exterior has ABS removable underbelly panels, a decorative front cap with a molded picket fence, an electric awning with LED night lighting, and a full, walk-on roof for added durability. The dual-pane patio door will allow you to see the beautiful outside scenery from the comfort of indoors, and the 8' 5" wide body will give your crew plenty of space to stretch out and relax. There are also vinyl floor coverings inside, along with solid surface countertops with stainless steel apron sinks, USB ports in the kitchen and bedroom, plus a spacious shower with a seat and sliding glass doors for added luxury.

Your guests can make themselves at home in the loft that includes a queen bed, a cabinet with shelves, and a table with space below for feet if you want to eat up here or play a board game!

units.description: Used 2017 Forest River RV Salem Villa Series 39FDEN Classic
units.details:
The Salem Villa Classic 39FDEN destination trailer by Forest River features double slides, dual entry, a queen bed, and a front living area.

As you enter the destination trailer, to the right there is an entertainment center. Along the front of the trailer there is a sofa with end tables on either side. The slide out has a lounge chair, sofa, and a dinette. Across from the slide there is a double kitchen sink, L-shaped counter with extra counter space, three burner range, residential refrigerator, and a pantry for your non-perishables.

Proceeding down the hall you will come to a side aisle bath. Inside the bathroom you will find a toilet, linen cabinet, shower, and a sink with medicine cabinet above.

In the rear of the trailer, in the bedroom there is a queen bed slide with nightstands on either side of the bed. Across from the bed there is a dresser. You will also find two wardrobes. One of the wardrobes can even have an optional washer and dryer. The bedroom also offers a private entrance door from the outside.

Outdoors you can enjoy a 21' awning, plus much more inside and out!

units.description: Used 2018 Grand Design Solitude 360RL
units.details:
You will find it easy to extend your stay awhile in this Grand Design Solitude fifth wheel model 360RL.  This unit features all of the amenities of home including a spacious kitchen with an 18 cu. ft. refrigerator, a kitchen island, an entertainment center with fireplace, and private front master bedroom, plus more!

Step inside and notice how open and spacious the kitchen is.  There are dual opposing slides in this area alone with the first slide to the left of the entry door featuring a free standing dinette.  Opposite you will find a slide out 18 cu. ft. refrigerator, a three burner range with overhead microwave oven, and overhead cabinetry with a bit of counter space.  You will love the center island which features a double sink, plenty of prep space, and it has also been prepped for a dishwasher. Add this option and spend more time outdoors rather than doing the dishes after each meal!  To finish out the kitchen, along the interior wall, you will find a pantry, plus more counter and storage space for your dry goods and daily dishes.

Head up the step to your right and find a side aisle bath and front master bedroom. The bath offers a shower with skylight and seat, a linen cabinet, a toilet, and vanity with sink. 

Just outside the bathroom there is a door to the front private bedroom.  Here you will enjoy plenty of room thanks to a slide out queen bed including a pull-out ottoman.  There is a full front wardrobe for your hanging clothes, shirt storage, a dresser, and a closet that has been prepped for a washer and dryer.  No pile of dirty laundry to take home here when you choose this option.

Back through to the rear of this unit you will find a living area including a slide out with theatre seating along the roadside, a slide out entertainment center with LED TV and fireplace opposite, plus a tri-fold sofa including overhead cabinets along the rear wall. This can also become added sleeping space for overnight guests.

Outside enjoy an exterior LED TV and refrigerator to keep cold drinks handy.  You will also love the unobstructed pass-through storage compartment for all of your outdoor camping items, plus universal docking station, and so much more!

This model is also available with a residential refrigerator.  Choose model 360RL R for this option.

You may choose to add a larger side-by-side refrigerator if you like. The convenient kitchen island provides a bit more counter space and dual sinks making cleanup and food prep a breeze.

Head right once inside the front entry door and notice the convenient coat closet on the left as you head up the steps to the top where you will find a full bath including: a toilet, vanity with vessel sink, linen cabinet, and 48" x 30" shower with seat.

Continue down the hall to the front master bedroom to a king size bed slide, pull-out ottoman at the foot of the bed, dresser opposite, the bed, and a walk-in closet with shirt storage on one side and a space prepped for a washer and dryer if you choose.

In this unit you can add an optional HDTV in the master bedroom, a stainless steel refrigerator, and a washer and dryer, plus so much more!

units.description: New 2026 Forest River RV Sierra 3800RK
units.details:
Forest River Sierra fifth wheel 3800RK highlights:

  • Four Slides
  • Theater Seating
  • Exterior Cooktop
  • Walk-In Bathroom Closet
  • 12V Refrigerator

 

If you're looking to go full-time RVing, this fifth wheel is packed with convenient features! The master bedroom includes a king bed slide out with USB ports on either side of the bed so you both can charge your phones, and there is a dresser for your folded clothes. You will love the front bathroom with dual bath sinks, a shower with a seat, plus a walk-in closet with shelves, rods to hand clothes, and baskets for laundry! There is a unique middle utility room with washer and dryer, Washer and dryer counter and a rod to hang clothes that will make a perfect laundry room, or you can utilize this space for storage! Head to the main living area to relax on the theater seating or hide-a-bed sofa, and if you have guests stay over, they can sleep here. There is also an entertainment center with a 50" flat screen TV, but you might just leave that off if you're working at the desk with a chair that is provided. We've saved the best part for last; the kitchen! Here, you'll find ample counter space to prep home-cooked meals, a three burner high output range with a 22" oven, plus a large counter with barstools where you can enjoy breakfast at each morning. Choosing this fifth wheel is a no-brainer!

 

Each one of these Forest River Sierra fifth wheels are equipped with everything you need to make the most of each adventure! The underbelly armor will protect your unit's vitals from road debris and the painted two tone aerodynamic fiberglass front cap has an improved turning radius to make them easier to navigate. With an electric leveling system, you can set your unit up quick and easy then get to having fun faster than ever. The welded aluminum framed, vacuum bonded laminated superstructure will hold up through every adventure and the cambered powder coated frame comes with rust prohibitor to last longer. Each model also includes the Summit Package that comes with a king Wi-Fi extender system and Olympus antenna, a full coach water filter system, Goodyear tires with 7,000 lb. axles, and the list goes on. The interior is just as impressive with rustic wood plank linoleum, recessed residential lighting, a memory foam mattress, and mocha accent crown molding over the kitchen cabinets!

There is a flip up table along the rear wall with a nearby 40" LED TV which features a butler pantry behind. Head up the steps to the right of the entry door to a complete bath and private front bedroom featuring a queen size bed with dual nightstands on both sides of the bed. The bathroom offers a shower with a skylight for added headroom and natural lighting. Outside, a 16' awning provides added living space protected from the elements!

 

The Cougar Sport structural I-beam frame with stamped steel cross-members and outriggers, plus its AlphaPly roof membrane are what active RVers love about the construction of the Cougar line. The Cougar Sport models are no exception when it comes to a great package, as well as being smaller and lighter weight than their big brother Cougar models. A one-piece, heated and enclosed polypropylene underbelly will add protection against the elements, and the electric stabilizer jacks will provide more stability. On the inside, residential shaker style hardwood cabinet doors and decorative crown molding, plus seamless pressed countertops and an on-demand water heater will make your unit feel even more like home. You are also sure to appreciate the shiplap style decorative accent wall behind the bed, a porcelain foot flush toilet in the bathroom, plus residential kitchen hardware, and so much more.

units.description: New 2026 Wayfinder RV GO LITE BOULDERBACK 14
units.details:
2026 Go Lite Boulderback 14: Compact Camping with Big Benefits

 

The Go Lite Boulderback 14 toy hauler travel trailer offers the functionality of a full-size RV in a lightweight, compact design that’s easy to tow with an SUV. It’s an excellent choice for adventurers who want to explore the great outdoors without upgrading their vehicle or dealing with the challenges of towing a large camper.

 

Key Features of the Go Lite Boulderback 14

Spacious Interior:

Despite its compact size, the Go Lite Boulderback 14 provides impressive space. The fold-up Murphy bed and pop-out tent expand the interior, creating a roomy and comfortable environment. Keep the back ramp door open with the magnetic screen in place to let in a refreshing breeze and stay connected to nature.

 

Lightweight and Easy to Tow:

With a UVW of just 2,380 pounds, the Go Lite is exceptionally lightweight, making it towable by smaller vehicles like SUVs, compact trucks, and some capable minivans. With an exterior length of only 16'2", its compact design allows you to access tight camping spots that larger RVs simply can’t reach.

 

Full Kitchen:

The Go Lite’s kitchen is thoughtfully designed to bring the comforts of home on the road. It features an 4.4-cubic-foot refrigerator and freezer, a full-sized residential farmhouse sink, a microwave, and a 2-burner stove, making cooking easy and enjoyable.

 

Adventure-Ready Design:

Built on a custom chassis tailored to its floorplan, the Go Lite Boulderback 14 offers extra support where it’s needed most. With an adjustable axle and heavy-duty off-road tires, this toy hauler is ready to take on rugged terrain and go wherever your adventures lead.

 

Why Choose Go Lite?

Go Lite redefines lightweight travel trailers, making adventure accessible to everyone. Weighing as little as 2,000 pounds, Go Lite trailers can be towed by most SUVs, V6 vehicles, and even minivans. Unlike other compact RVs, Go Lite combines affordability and functionality with essential features like a full kitchen, bathroom, and smart storage solutions. With Go Lite, you can embark on every adventure without compromise.

units.description: Used 2022 Keystone RV Fuzion Impact Edition 29V
units.details:
Keystone Fuzion Impact Edition Vapor Lite toy hauler 29V highlights:

  • U-Shaped Dinette
  • 10' Separate Garage
  • 8' Garage Door
  • Adjustable Bed
  • Dual Entry
  • Master Suite

 

Load up your toys, gear, clothing and food and head out to the off-road park to ride your toys and do it all over again the next day! You will appreciate the added space thanks to the double slides, and the 10' separate garage will provide a place for your toys and an area to prepare for rides as well as take a nap in between or even sleep if needed for overnight guests. The dual opposing sofas are in the garage and the U-shaped dinette slide is in the separate living/kitchen area. The chef of the group can prepare meals on the Furrion three-burner cooktop or in the microwave oven, and you can take your plate outdoors to sit under the 18' power awning with LED light strip. 

 

With any Fuzion Impact Edition toy hauler, the robust construction gives you years of enjoyment and the unexpected conveniences and technology allow you to enjoy the indoors while exploring outdoors on a budget!  Some standout features include the CNC sidewalls that are precision-routed to ensure the best possible seal around the windows, doors and slide boxes, the blade high-performance air flow system delivering an average of 20% more cooling power, and the 5k Interlock tie downs rated up to 5,000 lbs. each. The SolarFlex 200 delivers affordable, high quality solar energy and you can choose an option to upgrade if you like. While indoors, you will appreciate the full-extension ball bearing drawer guides, the pressed countertops, the hardwood cabinetry, the bedside outlets/USB to keep your electronics charged, and so much more providing comfort and convivence.  Choose an easy-to-tow, value-minded and impactful Fuzion Impact Edition toy hauler travel trailer or toy hauler fifth wheel today!

units.description: New 2024 Prime Time RV Avenger LE 24RKSLE
units.details:
Prime Time Avenger LE travel trailer 24RKSLE highlights:

  • Rear Kitchen
  • Private Bedroom
  • Pass-Through Storage
  • Large Slide

 

Enjoy each camping adventure with this Avenger LE model in tow! The rear kitchen is conveniently located near the entry door so packing up groceries and stocking the refrigerator is a breeze. You can easily cook up meals and snacks using the three burner cooktop and overhead microwave oven, and a nearby pantry will easily house all of your dry goods and snacks.  A single slide sofa and booth dinette offers ample seating when inside, plus adds an open floorplan to move about. A private front bedroom with a space saving sliding door provides cross ventilation with opposing windows, plus dual bedside wardrobes and an overhead shelf for your things. And, a full bath offers at-home conveniences with your own shower, toilet and sink, plus s medicine cabinet. No trips to the campground facilities in the middle of the night with this unit!

 

With any Avenger LE travel trailer by Prime Time RV you will enjoy at-home comforts while at the campground! Durable construction begins with an enclosed and heated underbelly, a one-piece roof membrane, and diamond plate front rock guard for added protection against debris during transport. There are also locking magnetic latches on the baggage doors, fully vented windows throughout, four stabilizer jacks, plus solar prep if you want the option to go off-grid. The interior will have you feeling right at home with residential extended ball bearing drawer glides, seamless Carefree Congoleum flooring, an XL single basin kitchen sink, and shower pans in all models that will make it easy to get in and out of the bath. Some of the convenient appliances and equipment you will appreciate are the 15,000 BTU A/C, 12V high-capacity water pump, Slim Profile range hood, and the Winegard 360+ antenna with Wi-Fi prep!

units.description: New 2025 Wayfinder RV Go Play 26RLS
units.details:
Dollar-for-dollar, Go>Play is the value-champ of travel trailers. Compare top camper brands like Cherokee, Coleman, Wildwood, and Jayco.

 

Call/text 1(844)646-7529 to confirm pricing and availability.

 

GO PLAY Interior

 

The Nordic Shore interior aesthetic seamlessly blends modern and contemporary elements. Leveraging lighter colors and durable materials, Go Play delivers a cozy interior without compromising structural integrity. 

 

Combining residential construction practices such as 16" on-center structural framing, cut & glued batten insulation, 5/8" thick tongue & groove floor decking with pocket-screwed, mortise & tenon cabinet construction with 75 lb. ball bearing drawer guides and hardwood cabinet doors to ensure durability and elegance. Pressed membrane kitchen countertops, a three-burner cooktop with a high output front burner, a double rack oven and microwave provide a sleek and easy-to-clean space for food prep while the range hood effectively removes smoke and odors from the kitchen. A residential high-rise faucet, single basin under-mount sink, 11cu/ft dual swing door 12V refrigerator, and residential vinyl flooring, with the flush floor slide, ensures practicality, making clean-up a breeze.

 

With an 81" ceiling height, a true 96" wide body, adjustable A/C vents, pleated blackout night shades, and LED internal lighting, the main living area is created with comfort in mind. The 13,500 BTU A/C and 25,000 BTU furnace provide robust flexibility for cozy camping through extended season camping, seldom found in the competitive set.

 

The bathroom features a foot flush toilet, a powered vent, and a full shower surround that gives plenty of room. The 6-gal gas/electric water heater provides hot water for the whole gang.

 

A collapsible u-shape dinette provides ample space for co-adventurers, while the front full-bed, nearby wardrobes, heavy duty struts for under bed storage, and barn sliding doors offers privacy for chaperones. A dome style digital TV antenna, and AM/FM/Bluetooth® radio with indoor/outdoor zoned speakers can keep you and loved ones entertained, making your Go>Play a perfect home away from home.

 

GO PLAY Exterior

 

A sleek black front diamond plate adds a touch of style and ensures durability while on the road. Dual axle models are equipped with an exterior docking center, making utility connection and camp set up a breeze. 

 

Experience safer towing with an elongated A-frame that provides increased stability and turning radius. For added security, the Go Play comes equipped with rear camera prep, self-adjusting electric brakes, and E-Z Lube® axles. The galvanized steel wheel wells help guard your coach from possible blowouts and nitrogen-filled radial tires provide stable air pressure throughout temperature and elevation changes. The nitrogen-filled radial tires also provide a smooth and stable ride, while the 200watt solar panel and 30amp charge controller allow you to harness the power of the sun for your adventures. The 1800W Inverter prep provides incredible flexibility for overlander or off-grid camping.

 

Go Play travel trailers come standard with the industry's most robust roof system, the Magnum roof system is fully walkable and rated up to 4,500 lbs. The magnetic baggage door catches and rain gutters with molded drip spouts help to keep your belongings safe and dry. The detachable power cords and flexible LP lines further add to the convenience of this travel trailer, allowing you to quickly and easily set up or break down camp. 

 

A full-sized electric awning for a wonderful outdoor experience.

 

The four stabilizer jacks, anti-slip solid steps and an entry grab handle provide added stability and security, while the thermal seal- enclosed, insulated, and heated underbelly and fully insulated roof ensure that you stay warm and comfortable no matter the weather. Tinted safety-glass windows throughout add a touch of elegance and protect you from harmful UV rays. The PVC roofing membrane is 20% more tear resistant and has 2x the puncture strength compared to the industry's standard membrane, adding even more durability and longevity to this impressive travel trailer.

 

*Shipping costs for home delivery are not included and will vary depending on the delivery address. Additionally, product pricing may also vary based on pick-up location due to factory proximity. Please contact us for shipping quotes and pricing confirmation.

units.description: New 2025 Wayfinder RV GO EXPLORE X252
units.details:
2025 Go Explore X252: Premium Camping, Practical Features

 

The Go Explore X252 family camper delivers an effortless camping experience with premium, practical features--without the premium price tag. It's an ideal choice for couples seeking both comfort and functionality in their RV, empowering you to focus on what matters most: exploring, making memories, and enjoying the journey with confidence.

Key Features of the Go Explore X252

Smarter Storage Solutions:

The industry-exclusive Super Suite bedroom in the Go Explore is a game-changer, featuring an under-bed storage system to keep all your belongings organized. The spacious pass-through storage compartment includes thoughtful additions like pegboards, a fishing rod holder, and more, making organizing effortless.

 

Practical Camping Features:

Go Explore travel trailers offer convenient camping features such as a dedicated trash can space, a laundry chute in the bedroom with a collapsible laundry basket, and strategically placed coat hooks and storage racks. On the exterior, two Kebloc hooks with attachments for an outdoor trash bag holder and towel rack help keep your RV space tidy and functional.

 

Chef's Kitchen:

The Go Explore's kitchen brings the comforts of home to the road. Features include a residential-sized farmhouse sink, removable sink covers, a built-in spice rack, knife storage, and a paper towel holder, making meal preparation while camping easy. 

 

Excellent Entryway:

Every Go Explore model features the industry's widest entry door, paired with an extra-large grab handle to make packing and unpacking easier. The solid steps include industry-exclusive built-in shoe storage, ensuring your shoes stay organized rather than cluttering your RV or campsite.

 

Pet-friendly Design:

Go Explore's pet friendly design means traveling with your pets is easier. It includes two exterior D-rings for securing pet leashes and a versatile pet rover station that can be mounted outside or brought indoors. The ventless and carpetless flooring makes cleaning up your RV quick and easy.  

 

Convenient Sanitation Station:

All your water and sewer hookups are conveniently located in one accessible area. The sanitation station includes a large storage box for hoses and gloves, along with an extra-wide tube for stowing your sewer hose. With everything in arms reach, it makes setting up and breaking down your campsite easier than ever.

 

Why Choose Go Explore?

Every Go Explore model is designed with intention, and every area of Go Explore RVs are made with the question, "How would someone actually use this, and how can we make it easier for them?"

We listened to real campers--people tired of digging through messy storage or wrestling awkward setups. We turned their frustrations into solutions: smart storage that keeps gear organized, comfort features that make every trip feel like home, and thoughtful innovations that make your trips effortless and stress-free. Go Explore ensures that you can enjoy your adventures with confidence and ease.
units.salesPitch: Pet Friendly! Smart Storage! Premium Camping with Practicality in Mind!

units.description: New 2025 Forest River RV Flagstaff E-Pro E15TB
units.details:
Forest River Flagstaff E-Pro travel trailer E15TB highlights:

  • Twin-Size Bed with King Conversion
  • Wet Bath
  • Outdoor Griddle
  • 10' Power Awning
  • Exterior Storage

 

It's time to hit the road in this small, yet walkable travel trailer that is versatile to your needs and offers everything you will want to stay comfortable at a campground or off-grid. You can make meals using the cooktop and microwave up front, and store your cold items in the 12V refrigerator. Take turns getting cleaned up in the wet bath so you can skip the public facilities, and store your clothing in the overhead cabinets. You can watch the 32" TV while dining or sleeping on the twin beds that offer a table top to help you convert this area into a king bed. And the 10' power awning will give you a place to hang out while you use the outdoor griddle.

 

With any Flagstaff E-Pro travel trailer by Forest River, you will experience lightweight towing, style and features that will meet your needs, plus amenities that give you more than you expected! Built with interior and exterior composite sidewall construction, tongue and grove plywood flooring, and a vacuum laminated roof and walls, plus torsion axle, Rubber-Ryde suspension, and a tire pressure monitoring system for safety while traveling. And the 200 watt roof mount solar panel with 1,800-watt inverter will allow you to stay off-grid if you like. The interior offers a comfortable environment with the choice to use the air conditioner or furnace, and a 12V entertainment TV with a stereo to stay up to date on your favorite movies. Make your selection today!
units.salesPitch: Compact & Easy to Tow!

units.description: New 2025 Wayfinder RV GO LITE SKYBREAKER
units.details:
2025 Go Lite Skybreaker: Tiny Trailer, Huge Experience

 

The Go Lite Skybreaker 12 travel trailer offers the functionality of a full-size RV in a lightweight, compact design that’s easy to tow with an SUV. It’s an excellent choice for adventurers who want to explore the great outdoors without upgrading their vehicle or dealing with the challenges of towing a large camper.

 

Key Features of the Go Lite Skybreaker 12

Spacious Interior:

The Go Lite Skybreaker 12 may be compact, but it’s loaded with features you'd expect in a much larger trailer. It comes equipped with a full kitchen, a dinette, a dry bath, a bunk bed, and a tent bed—providing three separate sleeping areas. You'll also enjoy tons of storage and panoramic windows that keep you connected to the great outdoors. It’s an awesome little model built for big adventures.

 

Lightweight and Easy to Tow:

With a UVW of just 2,300 pounds, the Go Lite is exceptionally lightweight, making it towable by smaller vehicles like SUVs, compact trucks, and some capable minivans. With an exterior length of only 13'10", its compact design allows you to access tight camping spots that larger RVs simply can’t reach.

 

Full Kitchen:

The Go Lite’s kitchen is thoughtfully designed to bring the comforts of home on the road. It features an 4.4-cubic-foot refrigerator and freezer, a full-sized residential farmhouse sink, a microwave, and a 2-burner stove, making cooking easy and enjoyable.

 

Adventure-Ready Design:

Built on a custom chassis tailored to its floorplan, the Go Lite Skybreaker 12 offers extra support where it’s needed most. With an adjustable axle and heavy-duty off-road tires, this trailer is ready to take on rugged terrain and go wherever your adventures lead.

 

Why Choose Go Lite?

Go Lite redefines lightweight travel trailers, making adventure accessible to everyone. Weighing as little as 2,000 pounds, Go Lite trailers can be towed by most SUVs, V6 vehicles, and even minivans. Unlike other compact RVs, Go Lite combines affordability and functionality with essential features like a full kitchen, bathroom, and smart storage solutions. With Go Lite, you can embark on every adventure without compromise.
units.salesPitch: EASY to TOW & Ready for Adventure!

units.description: New 2025 Wayfinder RV GO EXPLORE X225
units.details:
2025 Go Explore X225: Premium Camping, Practical Features

 

The Go Explore X225 couples camper delivers an effortless camping experience with premium, practical features--without the premium price tag. It's an ideal choice for couples seeking both comfort and functionality in their RV, empowering you to focus on what matters most: exploring, making memories, and enjoying the journey with confidence.

Key Features of the Go Explore X225

Smarter Storage Solutions:

The industry-exclusive Super Suite bedroom in the Go Explore is a game-changer, featuring an under-bed storage system to keep all your belongings organized. The spacious pass-through storage compartment includes thoughtful additions like pegboards, a fishing rod holder, and more, making organizing effortless.

 

Practical Camping Features:

Go Explore travel trailers offer convenient camping features such as a dedicated trash can space, a laundry chute in the bedroom with a collapsible laundry basket, and strategically placed coat hooks and storage racks. On the exterior, two Kebloc hooks with attachments for an outdoor trash bag holder and towel rack help keep your RV space tidy and functional.

 

Chef's Kitchen:

The Go Explore's kitchen brings the comforts of home to the road. Features include a residential-sized farmhouse sink, removable sink covers, a built-in spice rack, knife storage, and a paper towel holder, making meal preparation while camping easy. 

 

Excellent Entryway:

Every Go Explore model features the industry's widest entry door, paired with an extra-large grab handle to make packing and unpacking easier. The solid steps include industry-exclusive built-in shoe storage, ensuring your shoes stay organized rather than cluttering your RV or campsite.

 

Pet-friendly Design:

Go Explore's pet friendly design means traveling with your pets is easier. It includes two exterior D-rings for securing pet leashes and a versatile pet rover station that can be mounted outside or brought indoors. The ventless and carpetless flooring makes cleaning up your RV quick and easy.  

 

Convenient Sanitation Station:

All your water and sewer hookups are conveniently located in one accessible area. The sanitation station includes a large storage box for hoses and gloves, along with an extra-wide tube for stowing your sewer hose. With everything in arms reach, it makes setting up and breaking down your campsite easier than ever.

 

Why Choose Go Explore?

Every Go Explore model is designed with intention, and every area of Go Explore RVs are made with the question, "How would someone actually use this, and how can we make it easier for them?"

We listened to real campers--people tired of digging through messy storage or wrestling awkward setups. We turned their frustrations into solutions: smart storage that keeps gear organized, comfort features that make every trip feel like home, and thoughtful innovations that make your trips effortless and stress-free. Go Explore ensures that you can enjoy your adventures with confidence and ease.

units.description: New 2025 Wayfinder RV Go Play 26BH
units.details:
2025 Go Play 26BH: Affordable and Practical Camping

Go Play travel trailers are designed for families and first-time RVers seeking a durable, affordable camper that combines the must-have comforts of home with a feature-packed, family-friendly design. With space-saving layouts and rugged construction, these campers make camping simple, safe, and budget-friendly—so you can focus on having fun in the great outdoors.

 

Key Features of the Go Play 26BH

 

Camp-Ready

 

We believe when you purchase an RV it should be Camp-Ready. That’s why every Go Play is equipped with a 200-watt solar package and a heated and enclosed underbelly, so you can enjoy the freedom to camp whenever and wherever adventure takes you. 

 

Built For Durability

 

Every Go Play is built with the industry leading Magnum Truss Roof™ system, protecting your RV from damage while you’re camping. The hardwood lumber core cabinets with 70 lb. rated, full extension ball-bearing drawer glides ensure your RV is built with long-lasting durability.

 

Spacious, Functional Interiors

 

With an 8-foot-wide design and 6'9" ceilings, the Go Play provides more headroom and living space than many other conventional built travel trailers. Smart storage solutions and added features like coat and towel hooks, and a dedicated wastebasket space make every Go Play interior functional.

 

Tried and True

 

The 9 floor plans in the Go Play lineup cover over 70% of the industry’s best-selling floor plans, meaning you don’t have to worry whether every Go Play is a proven, customer-approved model. By sticking to tried and true floor plans we save on development costs for new designs you might not love—and pass those savings directly to you.

 

Super Suite Bedroom (available only in the 20FBS, 22MLS, 26BH, 26BHS, & 26RLS)

 

The Super Suite bedroom provides a more functional bedroom space. The bed utilizes 2 gas struts to lift, revealing 4 extra drawers, shoe storage, and an open space with a laundry basket to put your dirty laundry underneath the bed.

 

Why Choose Go Play?

 

Go Play was built by people who love camping and designed based on our experience and years of customer feedback. 

 

With a Go Play travel trailer, you’ll have everything you need to focus on what matters most—spending time with the people you love and creating memories that last a lifetime.?

units.description: New 2026 Wayfinder RV GO LITE SKYBREAKER
units.details:
2026 Go Lite Skybreaker 12: Tiny Trailer, Huge Experience

 

The Go Lite Skybreaker 12 travel trailer offers the functionality of a full-size RV in a lightweight, compact design that’s easy to tow with an SUV. It’s an excellent choice for adventurers who want to explore the great outdoors without upgrading their vehicle or dealing with the challenges of towing a large camper.

 

Key Features of the Go Lite Skybreaker 12

Spacious Interior:

The Go Lite Skybreaker 12 may be compact, but it’s loaded with features you'd expect in a much larger trailer. It comes equipped with a full kitchen, a dinette, a dry bath, a bunk bed, and a tent bed—providing three separate sleeping areas. You'll also enjoy tons of storage and panoramic windows that keep you connected to the great outdoors. It’s an awesome little model built for big adventures.

 

Lightweight and Easy to Tow:

With a UVW of just 2,300 pounds, the Go Lite is exceptionally lightweight, making it towable by smaller vehicles like SUVs, compact trucks, and some capable minivans. With an exterior length of only 13'10", its compact design allows you to access tight camping spots that larger RVs simply can’t reach.

 

Full Kitchen:

The Go Lite’s kitchen is thoughtfully designed to bring the comforts of home on the road. It features an 4.4-cubic-foot refrigerator and freezer, a full-sized residential farmhouse sink, a microwave, and a 2-burner stove, making cooking easy and enjoyable.

 

Adventure-Ready Design:

Built on a custom chassis tailored to its floorplan, the Go Lite Skybreaker 12 offers extra support where it’s needed most. With an adjustable axle and heavy-duty off-road tires, this trailer is ready to take on rugged terrain and go wherever your adventures lead.

 

Why Choose Go Lite?

Go Lite redefines lightweight travel trailers, making adventure accessible to everyone. Weighing as little as 2,000 pounds, Go Lite trailers can be towed by most SUVs, V6 vehicles, and even minivans. Unlike other compact RVs, Go Lite combines affordability and functionality with essential features like a full kitchen, bathroom, and smart storage solutions. With Go Lite, you can embark on every adventure without compromise.
units.salesPitch: Lightweight & Easy to Tow!

The Go Play 177BH Sport travel trailer is designed to be a more practical and affordable option for families looking to explore the outdoors. The Go Play Sport offers the same trusted quality and essential features that make Go Play great, but in a simplified, budget-friendly package.

Many budget-friendly travel trailers exclude a propane furnace, replacing it with a less efficient electric heater, and use side-mount AC units that struggle to cool effectively. The Go Play Sport stands out by including a propane furnace and a roof-mounted 13.5k BTU AC, ensuring you stay comfortable while camping.

Every Go Play is built with the industry leading Magnum Truss Roof™ system, protecting your RV from damage while you’re camping. The hardwood lumber core cabinets with 70 lb. rated, full extension ball-bearing drawer glides ensure your RV is built with long-lasting durability.

 

Spacious Interior:

With an 8-foot-wide body and 6’9” ceilings, the Go Play Sport is wider and taller than most competitive models from other manufacturers. This means the Go Play Sport provides more headroom and living space than many other budget-friendly travel trailers.

 

Why Choose Go Play Sport?

Go Play was built by people who love camping and designed based on our experience and years of customer feedback.

 

With a Go Play Sport travel trailer, you’ll have everything you need at a more affordable price, so you focus on what matters most—spending time with the people you love and creating memories that last a lifetime.

units.details:
Forest River Salem Cruise Lite travel trailer 26ICE highlights:

  • Front Private Bedroom
  • Large Slide Out
  • Pull-Out Drawers
  • Fireplace
  • Pass-Through Storage

 

You're sure to make camping memories in this spacious travel trailer! You can easily sleep eight people each night thanks to the double-size bunks, the custom king bed with Versa Tilt in the front bedroom plus the Versa-Lounge within the large slide out! The cooktop and microwave oven will let you make meals each day, and you'll appreciate the hidden pantry with shelves behind the fireplace. There is also a booth dinette where you can dine together or play a game of cards after dinner is cleaned up, or you may just find yourselves outdoors under the 18' awning with 4K blade lighting. And don't overlook the full bath, complete with a tub/shower that will make bath time easier if you have little ones. 

 

The Salem Cruise Lite travel trailers and toy haulers are value-minded units packed with great camping features! There are a variety of floorplans to choose from between two different regions. The enclosed Accessibelly will help protect against the elements and debris during transport, and the exterior retro/metal redesign is sure to be eye-catching! There are stylish roller shades inside, along with updated backsplash, elegant curtain rods and curtains, plus many more interior comforts! Choose a Salem Cruise Lite today for quality and value!

units.description: New 2026 Wayfinder RV Go Play 20FBS
units.details:
2026 Go Play 20FBS: Affordable and Practical Camping

Go Play travel trailers are designed for families and first-time RVers seeking a durable, affordable camper that combines the must-have comforts of home with a feature-packed, family-friendly design. With space-saving layouts and rugged construction, these campers make camping simple, safe, and budget-friendly—so you can focus on having fun in the great outdoors.

 

Key Features of the Go Play 20FBS

 

Camp-Ready

 

We believe when you purchase an RV it should be Camp-Ready. That’s why every Go Play is equipped with a 200-watt solar package and a heated and enclosed underbelly, so you can enjoy the freedom to camp whenever and wherever adventure takes you. 

 

Built For Durability

 

Every Go Play is built with the industry leading Magnum Truss Roof™ system, protecting your RV from damage while you’re camping. The hardwood lumber core cabinets with 70 lb. rated, full extension ball-bearing drawer glides ensure your RV is built with long-lasting durability.

 

Spacious, Functional Interiors

 

With an 8-foot-wide design and 6'9" ceilings, the Go Play provides more headroom and living space than many other conventional built travel trailers. Smart storage solutions and added features like coat and towel hooks, and a dedicated wastebasket space make every Go Play interior functional.

 

Tried and True

 

The 10 floor plans in the Go Play lineup cover over 70% of the industry’s best-selling floor plans, meaning you don’t have to worry whether every Go Play is a proven, customer-approved model. By sticking to tried and true floor plans we save on development costs for new designs you might not love—and pass those savings directly to you.

 

Super Suite Bedroom (available only in the 20FBS, 22MLS, 26BH, 26BHS, & 26RLS)

 

The Super Suite bedroom provides a more functional bedroom space. The bed utilizes 2 gas struts to lift, revealing 4 extra drawers, shoe storage, and an open space with a laundry basket to put your dirty laundry underneath the bed.

 

Why Choose Go Play?

 

Go Play was built by people who love camping and designed based on our experience and years of customer feedback. 

 

With a Go Play travel trailer, you’ll have everything you need to focus on what matters most—spending time with the people you love and creating memories that last a lifetime.?
units.salesPitch: Affordable & Luxury in one Convenient Package!

units.description: Used 2023 Forest River RV Rockwood GEO Pro G20BHS
units.details:
Forest River Rockwood Geo Pro travel trailer G20BHS highlights:

  • Exterior Storage
  • Full-Size Bed
  • 14' Power Awning
  • Dinette Slide Out
  • Bunk Beds

 

Your going to love camping with your family or friends in this largest bunk model in the GEO Pro lineup. The bunk beds will be perfect for little ones, while you take the front full-size bed. There is also a 44" booth dinette within the slide out for additional sleeping and seating space. The kitchen includes everything the chef will need to prepare meals each day, including a three burner cooktop, a microwave oven, and a 12V refrigerator for perishables. If the weather is nice, you may just find the chef outdoors cooking on the outside griddle under the 14' power awning. And check out the exterior bike door that will be perfect for bikes, luggage, or extra camp gear!

 

The Rockwood GEO Pro travel trailers and toy hauler by Forest River are ready for all your adventures. The interior and exterior Azdel construction, along with the vacuum laminated roof and walls provide a durable trailer, and the Dexter torsion axles with aluminum wheels make towing easier than ever. There are many convenient amenities, like the 13,500 BTU A/C, the Bluetooth system control panel, and the all-in-one Teton HD TV/WiFi/FM antenna with LTE prep. Each model includes frameless windows, fabric valances and roller shades, and a modern interior that will make you feel right at home. Everything you're looking for in your next RV is in a Rockwood GEO pro by Forest River!

units.description: Used 2019 Prime Time RV Avenger ATI 26BK
units.details:
Prime Time RV Avenger ATI travel trailer 26BK highlights:

  • Double-Size Bunks
  • Sofa
  • Ample Storage
  • Outdoor Kitchen
  • Sleeps Nine

 

This Avenger ATI travel trailer by Prime Time RV will have you and your family quickly enjoying time away from home! The outdoor kitchen is a "must have" feature when you love being in the great outdoors. You will also find full kitchen amenities inside. With the inclusion of a queen-size bed, sofa, booth dinette, and double-size bunks, there is plenty of room to sleep nine people each night, and the outdoor speakers give you an additional party area for everyone. 

 

With any Avenger ATI travel trailer, you will feel secure knowing that it has been made with exclusive Everlast construction, and the Dexter E-Z lube axles provide safety and peace of mind while traveling to your favorite locations. Once you have set up camp, you will appreciate the exterior shower that provides an extra place to clean off and the LED-lit power awning that lets you relax outside with family and friends.
units.salesPitch: Beautifully Pre-Owned Bunkhouse with Upgraded Bunk Mattresses, Convertible Sofa & a Queen Bed!

units.description: New 2026 Forest River RV Flagstaff Micro Lite 21FBRS
units.details:
Forest River Flagstaff Micro Lite travel trailer 21FBRS highlights:

  • Pass-Through Storage
  • RV Queen Bed
  • Single Slide
  • SolidStep Entry
  • 14' Power Awning with LED Lights

 

For the couple who is ready to get out and enjoy nature, this Flagstaff Micro Lite travel trailer is ideal for you! This unit has all of the basic amenities, like a rear corner bath with a radius shower, and a front RV queen bed that makes for a comfy night's rest. There is also flip-up storage under the bed to keep luggage, board games, and more! The slide out with the 72" sofa provides extra interior space so that you won't feel cramped. You'll also be able to enjoy your meals here with a table in front of the sofa. After swimming all day working up your appetite, come back to this unit and cook a meal on the three-burner cooktop! This travel trailer features a pass-through storage for your larger camping items, plus an exterior storage to hold the kids' outdoor games.

 

With any Flagstaff Micro Lite travel trailer by Forest River you will enjoy lightweight towing, durable construction, and added interior comforts to make each trip memorable! Each model features RoadTech tire pressure monitoring, Dexter Torflex axles, and nitrogen-filled Goodyear endurance tires for smooth towing from home to campground. The 6-sided aluminum framed construction provides a strong foundation so you can enjoy your RV for years to come, plus the radiant foil in the front cap, underbelly and slides help insulate your trailer. Additional exterior features include a 200W solar panel, back-up camera prep, frameless windows, and slam baggage doors. Each model includes the Great Expectations Package with roller shades, solid surface kitchen countertops, and hidden hinge cabinet doors. There is also an exterior hot/cold water port, outside speakers, a power tongue jack and stabilizer jacks, plus many more conveniences.
units.salesPitch: Keeping Camping Simple! Everything You Need PLUS!

units.description: Used 2023 Dutchmen RV Aspen Trail LE 25BH
units.details:
Dutchmen RV Aspen Trail LE travel trailer 25BH highlights:

  • Double-Size Bunks
  • Residential Queen Bed
  • Sofa
  • Rear Corner Bathroom
  • Power Awning

 

Enjoy privacy in the front bedroom when you close the curtains. You can sleep on your own residential queen bed, and there are two wardrobes to stow away your clothes. Your family and friends can sleep on the double-size bunks in the rear next to the full bathroom with a shower, and the booth dinette as well as the sofa provide extra sleeping space. The 7 cu. ft. refrigerator will hold your cold items, and you can cook using the range top, and keep everything clean using the galley sink with high rise faucet. And the overhead cabinets will hold your dishes, snacks and such.

 

With any Aspen Trail LE travel trailer by Dutchmen, you will have a durable roof structure with a TPO roof, 3/8" decking, fiberglass insulation, and an insulated structure with a metal exterior panel, a wood frame with R7 thermal insulation and a lauan interior panel, plus superior A/C cooling. The interior offers a Home Series interior design collection for an at home feel, full extension drawer guides throughout, mini blinds throughout for privacy, and LED interior lighting to see clearly day or night. Make your selection today and enjoy a smaller, lighter-weight RV!
units.salesPitch: Beautifully Pre-Owned Bunkhouse! Ready for Adventure!

units.description: Used 2019 Keystone RV Bullet Premier Ultra Lite 19FBPR
units.details:
Keystone Premier Ultra Lite 19FBPR travel trailer highlights:

  • Sleeps Four
  • Large Pass-Through
  • Rear Bathroom
  • In-Floor Heating
  • 12' Electric Awning
  • U-Shaped Dinette

 

If you own this Premier Ultra Lite travel trailer, you own a trailer that is truly a premium product. With its queen-size bed and U-shaped booth dinette, this trailer is able to sleep four people while on the road, and the large wardrobe spaces that are located in both the front bedroom area and the rear bathroom give you plenty of room to travel with all of your personal toiletries and clothing accessories. 

 

Because of the innovative and modern approach that Keystone has taken with the construction of the Premier travel trailer, you receive a unit that is both functional and comfortable. The residential in-floor heating system gives the stain-resistant Beauflor linoleum flooring a warm and cozy touch, and the 6' 11" vaulted ceilings keep the entire trailer open and inviting to all guests. If you enjoy hosting late-night get togethers with those guests, then the outdoor electric awning with LED lights is a perfect spot for you and your friends to get together as you listen to your favorite music on the exterior speakers.
units.salesPitch: Beautifully Pre-Owned & Ready for Adventure! Convertible Dinette & Rear Bath!

units.description: Used 2018 Winnebago Industries Towables Minnie 2401 RG
units.details:
Winnebago Industries Towables Minnie travel trailer 2401RG highlights:

  • Rear Kitchen Layout
  • Single Slide Out
  • Abundant Storage
  • Dual Entry/Exit Doors
  • Private Bedroom

 

The rear kitchen layout really makes this Minnie travel trailer unique.  You will find it easy and fun to cook while you camp, and dining will be comfortable at the booth dinette inside. You can also choose to take your meals out on a warm sunny day and enjoy the sites and sounds while you eat at a camp picnic table or under the power awning in the shade. There is abundant storage throughout with overhead cabinets, plus wardrobes, as well as in lockable storage spaces on the exterior where you can tuck away outdoor toys, games, and gear.  You will also find an outdoor shower which is great for rinsing off before heading inside.  The rear private bedroom also features it's own private entry door making it convenient to slip out for a moonlit stroll on a warm clear night!

 

In any Minnie travel trailer by Winnebago Industries Towables you will find increased living space with a fantastic single slide out, plus abundant storage and livability throughout these vary functional floorplan layouts.  Each Minnie is expertly constructed starting with a BAL engineered chassis designed with strength to weight ratio, rust protection, and durability.  Next, tongue and groove plywood flooring is fastened onto the chassis providing the best foundation for all furniture and cabinetry. The welded aluminum tube sidewall frame features solid inserts where needed for attachments which keeps the weight light enough to be towed by your family SUV or small truck easily, and you can choose from eight colors of Noble classic T60 high gloss fiberglass to match your personality and style, or maybe you just want to make a statement when you pull into the campground!  On the inside, you will find each Minnie trailer to be full of life with light colored interiors along with efficient LED lighting, complete kitchen and bath accommodations, plus ample storage and so much more!
units.salesPitch: Beautifully Pre-Owned & Ready for Adventure! Dual Entry & Rear Kitchen!

units.description: New 2026 Wayfinder RV Go Play 26BHS
units.details:
2026 Go Play 26BHS: Affordable and Practical Camping

Go Play travel trailers are designed for families and first-time RVers seeking a durable, affordable camper that combines the must-have comforts of home with a feature-packed, family-friendly design. With space-saving layouts and rugged construction, these campers make camping simple, safe, and budget-friendly—so you can focus on having fun in the great outdoors.

 

Key Features of the Go Play 26BHS

 

Camp-Ready

 

We believe when you purchase an RV it should be Camp-Ready. That’s why every Go Play is equipped with a 200-watt solar package and a heated and enclosed underbelly, so you can enjoy the freedom to camp whenever and wherever adventure takes you. 

 

Built For Durability

 

Every Go Play is built with the industry leading Magnum Truss Roof™ system, protecting your RV from damage while you’re camping. The hardwood lumber core cabinets with 70 lb. rated, full extension ball-bearing drawer glides ensure your RV is built with long-lasting durability.

 

Spacious, Functional Interiors

 

With an 8-foot-wide design and 6'9" ceilings, the Go Play provides more headroom and living space than many other conventional built travel trailers. Smart storage solutions and added features like coat and towel hooks, and a dedicated wastebasket space make every Go Play interior functional.

 

Tried and True

 

The 10 floor plans in the Go Play lineup cover over 70% of the industry’s best-selling floor plans, meaning you don’t have to worry whether every Go Play is a proven, customer-approved model. By sticking to tried and true floor plans we save on development costs for new designs you might not love—and pass those savings directly to you.

 

Super Suite Bedroom (available only in the 20FBS, 22MLS, 26BH, 26BHS, & 26RLS)

 

The Super Suite bedroom provides a more functional bedroom space. The bed utilizes 2 gas struts to lift, revealing 4 extra drawers, shoe storage, and an open space with a laundry basket to put your dirty laundry underneath the bed.

 

Why Choose Go Play?

 

Go Play was built by people who love camping and designed based on our experience and years of customer feedback. 

 

With a Go Play travel trailer, you’ll have everything you need to focus on what matters most—spending time with the people you love and creating memories that last a lifetime.?
units.salesPitch: Affordable & Practical Bunkhouse!

units.description: New 2026 Wayfinder RV GO LITE LTD Solo
units.details:
2026 Go Lite Solo: Simple and Camp Ready Rig for the Solo Adventurer

 

The Go Lite Solo travel trailer offers the functionality of a full-size RV in a lightweight, compact design that’s easy to tow with an SUV. It’s an excellent choice for adventurers who want to explore the great outdoors without upgrading their vehicle or dealing with the challenges of towing a large camper.

 

Key Features of the Go Lite Solo

Practical Design:

The innovative design of the Go Lite Solo provides an impressive amount of practical camping features that you won't find in other RVs of this size. Outside the Solo, you'll find a full kitchen, inside it is simply your sleeping solution and smart storage solutions. Get ready to get on the road!

 

Lightweight and Easy to Tow:

With a UVW of just 1,793 pounds, the Solo is exceptionally lightweight, making it towable by smaller vehicles like SUVs, compact trucks, and some capable minivans. With an exterior length of only 13'8", its compact design allows you to access tight camping spots that larger RVs simply can’t reach.

 

Adventure-Ready Design:

Built on a custom chassis tailored to its floorplan, the Go Lite Solo offers extra support where it’s needed most. With an adjustable axle and heavy-duty off-road tires, this travel trailer is ready to take on rugged terrain and go wherever your adventures lead.

 

Why Choose Go Lite?

Go Lite redefines lightweight travel trailers, making adventure accessible to everyone. Weighing as little as 2,000 pounds, Go Lite trailers can be towed by most SUVs, V6 vehicles, and even minivans. Unlike other compact RVs, Go Lite combines affordability and functionality with essential features like a full kitchen, bathroom, and smart storage solutions. With Go Lite, you can embark on every adventure without compromise.
units.salesPitch: Lightweight & Easy to Tow! Solo Camping Has Never Been Easier!

units.description: Used 2021 Grand Design Imagine 2500RL
units.details:
Grand Design Imagine travel trailer 2500RL highlights:
  • Walk-Through Bath
  • Dual Entry
  • U-Shaped Dinette
  • Removable Ottoman
  • Solar Power Inlet
  • Power Tongue Jack
 
You and your spouse will love this trailer with its master suite in the front which includes the second exterior entry, and a space savings sliding interior door with quick access to the walk-through bathroom.  You can dine at the U-shaped dinette with removable ottoman to relax your legs or choose the optional free standing dinette in its place.  The rear tri-fold sofa gives you a place to unwind after hiking the trials or making dinner in the L-shaped kitchen which includes a counter extension for extra space to dry dishes or serve food.  And the LED TV provides inside entertainment with a pantry behind it to hold all your snacks.
 
With any Imagine by Grand Design the construction includes a laminated aluminum framed main floor, rear wall, side walls, roof and end walls in the slide rooms and floors, plus a one-piece roof membrane giving you years of lightweight towing to your favorite destinations.  Best in class storage is found in the exclusive drop frame unobstructed pass through storage, and the Universal Docking station offers an all-in-one location for utilities and hookups, plus you will find industry leading tank capacities and extended season camping with the mandatory four-season protection package. Inside you will experience residential cabinetry and a pull-down sprayer kitchen faucet, upgraded residential furniture and countertops, plus much more with an 81" radius ceiling for a spacious interior.  Choose your favorite Imagine today, and start adventuring in a lightweight and comfortable trailer!
units.salesPitch: Beautifully Pre-Owned & Ready for Adventure! Lots of Storage & Plenty of Living Space for a Couples Weekend Away!

units.description: Used 2021 Coachmen RV Freedom Express Ultra Lite 257BHS
units.details:
Coachmen Freedom Express Ultra Lite travel trailer 257BHS highlights:

  • Double-Size Bunks
  • Single Slide
  • U-Shaped Dinette
  • Queen Bed with Vaulted Storage
  • Outdoor Kitchen

units.description: New 2026 Wayfinder RV Go Play 26BHS
units.details:
2026 Go Play 26BHS: Affordable and Practical Camping

Go Play travel trailers are designed for families and first-time RVers seeking a durable, affordable camper that combines the must-have comforts of home with a feature-packed, family-friendly design. With space-saving layouts and rugged construction, these campers make camping simple, safe, and budget-friendly—so you can focus on having fun in the great outdoors.

 

Key Features of the Go Play 26BHS

 

Camp-Ready

 

We believe when you purchase an RV it should be Camp-Ready. That’s why every Go Play is equipped with a 200-watt solar package and a heated and enclosed underbelly, so you can enjoy the freedom to camp whenever and wherever adventure takes you. 

 

Built For Durability

 

Every Go Play is built with the industry leading Magnum Truss Roof™ system, protecting your RV from damage while you’re camping. The hardwood lumber core cabinets with 70 lb. rated, full extension ball-bearing drawer glides ensure your RV is built with long-lasting durability.

 

Spacious, Functional Interiors

 

With an 8-foot-wide design and 6'9" ceilings, the Go Play provides more headroom and living space than many other conventional built travel trailers. Smart storage solutions and added features like coat and towel hooks, and a dedicated wastebasket space make every Go Play interior functional.

 

Tried and True

 

The 10 floor plans in the Go Play lineup cover over 70% of the industry’s best-selling floor plans, meaning you don’t have to worry whether every Go Play is a proven, customer-approved model. By sticking to tried and true floor plans we save on development costs for new designs you might not love—and pass those savings directly to you.

 

Super Suite Bedroom (available only in the 20FBS, 22MLS, 26BH, 26BHS, & 26RLS)

 

The Super Suite bedroom provides a more functional bedroom space. The bed utilizes 2 gas struts to lift, revealing 4 extra drawers, shoe storage, and an open space with a laundry basket to put your dirty laundry underneath the bed.

 

Why Choose Go Play?

 

Go Play was built by people who love camping and designed based on our experience and years of customer feedback. 

 

With a Go Play travel trailer, you’ll have everything you need to focus on what matters most—spending time with the people you love and creating memories that last a lifetime.?

units.description: New 2026 Wayfinder RV GO LITE LTD Solo
units.details:
2026 Go Lite Solo: Simple and Camp Ready Rig for the Solo Adventurer

 

The Go Lite Solo travel trailer offers the functionality of a full-size RV in a lightweight, compact design that’s easy to tow with an SUV. It’s an excellent choice for adventurers who want to explore the great outdoors without upgrading their vehicle or dealing with the challenges of towing a large camper.

 

Key Features of the Go Lite Solo

Practical Design:

The innovative design of the Go Lite Solo provides an impressive amount of practical camping features that you won't find in other RVs of this size. Outside the Solo, you'll find a full kitchen, inside it is simply your sleeping solution and smart storage solutions. Get ready to get on the road!

 

Lightweight and Easy to Tow:

With a UVW of just 1,793 pounds, the Solo is exceptionally lightweight, making it towable by smaller vehicles like SUVs, compact trucks, and some capable minivans. With an exterior length of only 13'8", its compact design allows you to access tight camping spots that larger RVs simply can’t reach.

 

Adventure-Ready Design:

Built on a custom chassis tailored to its floorplan, the Go Lite Solo offers extra support where it’s needed most. With an adjustable axle and heavy-duty off-road tires, this travel trailer is ready to take on rugged terrain and go wherever your adventures lead.

 

Why Choose Go Lite?

Go Lite redefines lightweight travel trailers, making adventure accessible to everyone. Weighing as little as 2,000 pounds, Go Lite trailers can be towed by most SUVs, V6 vehicles, and even minivans. Unlike other compact RVs, Go Lite combines affordability and functionality with essential features like a full kitchen, bathroom, and smart storage solutions. With Go Lite, you can embark on every adventure without compromise.

units.description: New 2026 Wayfinder RV Go Play 19BH-G
units.details:
2026 Go Play 19BH: Affordable and Practical Camping

Go Play travel trailers are designed for families and first-time RVers seeking a durable, affordable camper that combines the must-have comforts of home with a feature-packed, family-friendly design. With space-saving layouts and rugged construction, these campers make camping simple, safe, and budget-friendly—so you can focus on having fun in the great outdoors.

 

Key Features of the Go Play 19BH

 

Camp-Ready

 

We believe when you purchase an RV it should be Camp-Ready. That’s why every Go Play is equipped with a 200-watt solar package and a heated and enclosed underbelly, so you can enjoy the freedom to camp whenever and wherever adventure takes you. 

 

Built For Durability

 

Every Go Play is built with the industry leading Magnum Truss Roof™ system, protecting your RV from damage while you’re camping. The hardwood lumber core cabinets with 70 lb. rated, full extension ball-bearing drawer glides ensure your RV is built with long-lasting durability.

 

Spacious, Functional Interiors

 

With an 8-foot-wide design and 6'9" ceilings, the Go Play provides more headroom and living space than many other conventional built travel trailers. Smart storage solutions and added features like coat and towel hooks, and a dedicated wastebasket space make every Go Play interior functional.

 

Tried and True

 

The 9 floor plans in the Go Play lineup cover over 70% of the industry’s best-selling floor plans, meaning you don’t have to worry whether every Go Play is a proven, customer-approved model. By sticking to tried and true floor plans we save on development costs for new designs you might not love—and pass those savings directly to you.

 

Super Suite Bedroom (available only in the 20FBS, 22MLS, 26BH, 26BHS, & 26RLS)

 

The Super Suite bedroom provides a more functional bedroom space. The bed utilizes 2 gas struts to lift, revealing 4 extra drawers, shoe storage, and an open space with a laundry basket to put your dirty laundry underneath the bed.

 

Why Choose Go Play?

 

Go Play was built by people who love camping and designed based on our experience and years of customer feedback. 

 

With a Go Play travel trailer, you’ll have everything you need to focus on what matters most—spending time with the people you love and creating memories that last a lifetime.?

units.description: Used 2021 Forest River RV Flagstaff Super Lite 29RBS
units.details:
Forest River Flagstaff Super Lite travel trailer 29RBS highlights:

  • Bath Walk-In Closet
  • Bedroom Window Seating
  • Queen Bed Slide
  • Booth Dinette
  • Outside Kitchen

 

How does having a full rear bathroom with a unique walk-in closet for more privacy and storage, plus a space prepped for a washer/dryer option sound in your next couple's trailer?  After getting cleaned up after your long hike, you and your spouse can cozy up on the 67" hide-a-bed sofa or dine at the 44" booth dinette all while staying warm from the fireplace.  You will have full kitchen amenities to make meals when you like, and a front bedroom with unique window seating and wardrobe storage.  There is even an outside kitchen to utilize for a few meals, a 21' power awning offering an outdoor living area, plus a pass-through storage for your larger outdoor gear.

 

With any Flagstaff Super Lite travel trailer by Forest River you will experience a lightweight RV that is built with a 6 sided aluminum cage construction, vacuum laminated one-piece roof and walls, laminated fiberglass sidewalls, and an enclosed underbelly for four seasons of camping.  The interior is just as impressive with a Shower Miser water saver system, hardwood cabinet doors and drawers, undermount double bowl kitchen sink with a residential style faucet, ceiling LED 12 volt interior lighting, and a monitor panel switch station with a OneControl app.  Make your selection today!
units.salesPitch: Beautifully Pre-Owned & Ready for Adventure! Features a Walk-In Closet, Tons of Storage, Outside Kitchen, & MORE!

units.description: New 2026 Forest River RV Flagstaff E-Pro E19FD
units.details:
Forest River Flagstaff E-Pro travel trailer E19FD highlights:

  • Murphy Bed
  • 32" Booth Dinette
  • Rear Full Bath
  • Pass-Through Storage

 

Whether you enjoy staying at the campground for a weekend or longer and/or you enjoy off-grid camping, this 20' 2" long trailer gives you lots of interior space and versatility to enjoy each and every trip. From the Murphy bed/sofa combo up front offering sleeping space and seating depending on which you prefer at the time, to the full rear bathroom which also offers overhead storage, you will have everything you need. And the kitchen cooktop, microwave and 12V refrigerator allow you to make meals and store leftovers. Two can dine at the booth dinette or you can eat outdoors under the 14' power awning.

 

With any Flagstaff E-Pro travel trailer by Forest River, you will experience lightweight towing, style and features that will meet your needs, plus amenities that give you more than you expected! Built with interior and exterior composite sidewall construction for added strength and durability, a fully laminated roof for weather-tight protection, and aluminum truss roof bracing for enhanced stability.  These trailers are equipped with Dexter leaf-spring axles for smooth towing and durable performance. The interior features an aluminum dinette, bed, and bunk, providing a strong and lightweight framework for comfortable living. Additionally, the backup camera prep ensures a safe and stress-free reversing experience. Make your selection today!

units.description: New 2026 Forest River RV Flagstaff Super Lite 29RLKS
units.details:
Forest River Flagstaff Super Lite travel trailer 29RLKS highlights:

  • Kitchen Island
  • Queen Bed
  • Two Power Awnings
  • 44" Booth Dinette

 

You'll feel right at home when staying in this spacious travel trailer. There are dual opposing slides in the combined kitchen and living area, and the large kitchen island will give the chef of your group more counter space to prep meals. Your crew can dine at the booth dinette, relax on the theater seat, and sleep on the hide-a-bed sofa. You'll find your own space in the front private bedroom that includes a queen bed, triple wardrobes, and a TV option. Head outdoors to find two power awnings, a rear 2" receiver hitch, and a pass-thru storage with an optional steel sliding tray. 

 

With any Flagstaff Super Lite travel trailer by Forest River, you can enjoy quality features with lightweight towing! The Climate Protection Package includes radiant foil in the front cap, underbelly, and slides, plus there are 12V thermostat-controlled heated tanks for added protection. The complete composite wall construction and 6-sided full-aluminum frame is ultra durable, and the RoadTech tire pressure monitoring adds safety. Each model also includes the Coast to Coast Package that comes with slam latch baggage doors, a high gloss fiberglass cap, Goodyear Endurance tires, plus a 200W solar panel with an optional additional 200W panel for more off grid capabilities. Inside, you'll love the roller shades, solid surface kitchen countertops, a shower miser system, and many more comforts!

units.description: Used 2014 Jayco Jay Flight Swift 267BHS
units.details:
The Jay Flight Swift 267BHS travel trailer by Jayco offers a single slide with more room for your family.

The kitchen and living areas offer a sofa and dinette slide on one side and a double kitchen sink, three burner range, microwave, refrigerator, and wardrobe on the other side. There is a nice size entertainment center that you can easily view from anywhere in the kitchen and living area.

units.description: New 2026 Wayfinder RV GO EXPLORE LTD 233ML
units.details:
Go Explore Limited Series 233ML highlights:

  • Rear Kitchen
  • Front Bedroom
  • Dual Entry Doors
  • Outside Storage
  • Docking Station

 

It is easy to enter and exit this travel trailer with the dual entry doors! One of the entrances leads directly into the front private bedroom which has a queen bed with wardrobes on either side, and the other entrance leads into the rear kitchen where you can prepare your best home cooked meals. Enjoy your meals at the booth dinette then play a card game or relax on the tri-fold sofa. Rinse the sand out of your hair with the shower in the full bathroom and keep your towel close by with the linen closet. Enjoy your beautiful scenery rain or shine as you relax in a chair underneath the 21' power awning! 

 

Each one of these Go Explore Limited Series travel trailers maximize their interior space while staying lightweight thanks to the TuffShell fiberglass walls! The residential floor slides create more interior space, and the residential vinyl flooring throughout makes them kid and pet friendly. A few construction features you will appreciate include a fully-walkable roof, a thermal seal which means the underbelly is enclosed, heated, and insulated, and a fully insulated roof with a PVC roofing membrane. Plus, there is an exterior grill hookup quick connect port, self-adjusting electric brakes to help you safely arrive, and an oversized pass-through storage area with motion lighting. Each model also includes the Xtend Solar I Package with a 200 watt solar panel with a 30 amp solar controller so boondocking is easier than ever. 

 

Wayfinder RV Limited Series

At Wayfinder RV, our mission is to design RVs that our customers truly love. We listen to real RVers like you to build smarter, more comfortable, and more capable campers. 

 

That’s why we created the Wayfinder RV Limited Series, exclusive models that let us bring your feedback to life.

 

What is the Wayfinder RV Limited Series?

  • Exclusive, limited-run models: These campers are designed to test new features, floor plans, RV types, and price points based on your input.
  • Real-world feedback: The Limited Series helps us gather valuable insights from our customers on what they love most in an RV.
  • Possibility of return: Popular models with great feedback may return in the future as part of our main lineup, but that’s not guaranteed.

 

Be among the first to try out features that could shape the future of RV camping!
units.salesPitch: LIMITED SERIES! Features Private Queen Bedroom, Rear Kitchen, and MORE!

units.description: Used 2022 Jayco Jay Flight 34RSBS
units.details:
Jayco Jay Flight travel trailer 34RSBS highlights:

  • Theater Seating
  • Jackknife Sofa
  • Kitchen Island
  • Fireplace
  • Master Suite
  • Hutch

 

This Jay Flight travel trailer is very similar to model 34RLOK with just a few tweaks! The fireplace sits below the entertainment center, and both items are across from the theater seating. You'll also have a jackknife sofa right there so that others can join in on the relaxation, and the booth dinette is situated next to the theater seating so that it can also be used as seating during movie nights. A kitchen island adds function to the kitchen, and it also serves as a great dishwashing station. You can cook just about anything on the three-burner range, and the pantry will help you store your snacks. You'll also be able to access the dual-entry bathroom from the main hallway or the front bedroom. 

 

Check out the #1-selling Jayco Jay flight travel trailer! These trailers are built upon I-Class™ cambered structural steel I-beams and a fully integrated A-frame. They have axles with electric, self-adjusting brakes and easy-lube hubs to make your journeys smooth, and the Magnum Truss roof system will withstand many years and types of travel. You'll have large exterior downspouts, a front diamond plate, four stabilizer jacks, and a friction-hinge entry door with shade-prep window. The interior is where you'll find great comfort and modern design. There are residential-style kitchen countertops, solid hardwood cabinet doors, a premium multimedia sound system, a full-height kitchen backsplash, a kitchen skylight with shade, and a deluxe bedspread with pillows.

units.description: Used 2021 KZ Connect SE C281BHSE
units.details:
KZ Connect SE travel trailer C281BHSE highlights:

  • Rear Bunk Beds
  • Dual Entry
  • U-Dinette Dinette
  • Walk-Through Bath
  • Dual Pass-Through Storage

 

If you are looking for lots of interior space as well as sleeping space for eight to nine campers, you have found it in this Connect SE travel trailer! From the rear set of bunk beds, a 70" sofa and a U-shaped dinette in the main living area, plus a queen bed in the private bedroom, there is room for everyone to get a good night's rest. Some of the conveniences you will surely love include dual entry doors giving you easy access to the main area and the front bedroom, a walk-through bathroom with linen storage and extra counter space for everyone's toiletries, and an L-shaped kitchen with full amenities. Outside, there is a pass-through storage in the front and the rear of the trailer allowing you to take everything you need with you each trip. So load up the family and start making memories!

 

The NXG frame foundation for each Connect SE travel trailer by KZ is just as impressive as its interior since it is constructed with high-strength low-alloy prime steel, uses the CNC controlled rail fabrications and camber, plus eliminates frame failures, construction issues, and corrosion! The exterior also includes a one-piece seamless, walk-on roof that has Tufflex roofing material, UVA and UVB-resistant gelcoat Lamilux® exterior, 3/8" fully walk-on roof decking and a heated, insulated and enclosed underbelly giving you freedom to travel during any climate. Some of the interior features that are sure to impress include Rich Woodbridge maple cabinetry, hand-crafted mortise and tenon cabinet doors, accent trim on corners and entry door, a matte black residential kitchen faucet, and much more! Choose a lightweight, low-priced Connect SE today!

There is a full bathroom for convenience when changing and getting cleaned up, a galley kitchen with a two burner cooktop plus a 3.3 cu. ft. refrigerator for the cold items. And you can stow your larger camping items in the exterior pass-through compartment.

Each model features an aluminum exterior, tinted safety glass windows, and an I-beam frame with stamped steel cross-members and outriggers for added support. The interior includes blackout night shades for added privacy and real wood doors and drawers that will give a more at-home touch. The Girard tankless water heater is a feature you won't want to camp without, and the LED lighting will keep your space bright and open!

Get ready for comfort and style in a Sonic ultra-lightweight, tandem-axle travel trailer of your choice!

units.description: New 2026 Wayfinder RV GO BEYOND LTD 171FD
units.details:
2026 Go Beyond LTD 171FD: Comfortable Camping in a Compact Camper

 

The Go Beyond LTD 171FD travel trailer offers the functionality of a full-size RV in a lightweight, compact design that’s easy to tow with an SUV. It’s an excellent choice for adventurers who want to explore the great outdoors without upgrading their vehicle or dealing with the challenges of towing a large camper. Keep in mind, these are our limited series, a prototype run that allows us to try out all of the suggestions that you have for better RVs. This is a very limited run, and once they're gone, they're gone. 

 

Key Features of the Go Beyond LTD 171FD

Innovative & Practical Design:

The innovative design of the Go Beyond LTD 171FD provides an impressive amount of practical camping features that you won't find in other RVs of this size. Inside the Go Beyond, you'll find a full kitchen with a dinette, unique bathroom, dedicated queen bed, and loads of storage. 

 

Lightweight and Easy to Tow:

With a UVW of just 2,646 pounds, the 171FD is lightweight, making it towable by smaller vehicles like SUVs, compact trucks, and some capable minivans. With an exterior length of only 24", its not too long and allows you to access tight camping spots that larger RVs simply can’t reach.

 

Full Kitchen:

The Go Beyond’s kitchen is thoughtfully designed to bring the comforts of home on the road. It features a 4.4-cubic-foot refrigerator and freezer, a microwave, and a 2-burner stove, making cooking easy and enjoyable.

 

Adventure-Ready Design:

With strong wheel-wells and heavy-duty off-road tires, and an onboard 100W solar panel to recharge your batteries off-grid, this travel trailer is ready to take on rugged terrain and go wherever your adventures lead.

Tons of Storage

 

The Go Beyond LTD 171FD has an amount of storage that is unparallel. Spanning most of the length of the RV, you can fit brooms, fishing pools, totes, anything that you need to make camping memorable. 

 

At Wayfinder RV, our mission is to design RVs that our customers truly love. We listen to real RVers like you to build smarter, more comfortable, and more capable campers.
