units.description: New 2026 Wayfinder RV GO BEYOND LTD 171FD
units.details:
2026 Go Beyond LTD 171FD: Comfortable Camping in a Compact Camper

 

The Go Beyond LTD 171FD travel trailer offers the functionality of a full-size RV in a lightweight, compact design that’s easy to tow with an SUV. It’s an excellent choice for adventurers who want to explore the great outdoors without upgrading their vehicle or dealing with the challenges of towing a large camper. Keep in mind, these are our limited series, a prototype run that allows us to try out all of the suggestions that you have for better RVs. This is a very limited run, and once they're gone, they're gone. 

 

Key Features of the Go Beyond LTD 171FD

Innovative & Practical Design:

The innovative design of the Go Beyond LTD 171FD provides an impressive amount of practical camping features that you won't find in other RVs of this size. Inside the Go Beyond, you'll find a full kitchen with a dinette, unique bathroom, dedicated queen bed, and loads of storage. 

 

Lightweight and Easy to Tow:

With a UVW of just 2,646 pounds, the 171FD is lightweight, making it towable by smaller vehicles like SUVs, compact trucks, and some capable minivans. With an exterior length of only 24", its not too long and allows you to access tight camping spots that larger RVs simply can’t reach.

 

Full Kitchen:

The Go Beyond’s kitchen is thoughtfully designed to bring the comforts of home on the road. It features a 4.4-cubic-foot refrigerator and freezer, a microwave, and a 2-burner stove, making cooking easy and enjoyable.

 

Adventure-Ready Design:

With strong wheel-wells and heavy-duty off-road tires, and an onboard 100W solar panel to recharge your batteries off-grid, this travel trailer is ready to take on rugged terrain and go wherever your adventures lead.

Tons of Storage

 

The Go Beyond LTD 171FD has an amount of storage that is unparallel. Spanning most of the length of the RV, you can fit brooms, fishing pools, totes, anything that you need to make camping memorable.

units.details:
2026 Soaring Eagle AERIE 8 – Lightweight Luxury for Full-Size Trucks

Experience true freedom on the road with the new 2026 Soaring Eagle AERIE 8 — a premium hard-side truck camper designed for ¾-ton and 1-ton trucks with 8-foot beds. Built with welded aluminum framing and composite materials, the AERIE 8 offers strength, durability, and all-season comfort without unnecessary weight.

Key Features:

  • Approx. 2,300 lbs dry weight — perfect for full-size long-bed trucks

  • All-aluminum and composite construction — no wood, no rot

  • Fully enclosed, heated basement for four-season camping

  • Spacious wet bath with 40” x 40” shower and cassette toilet

  • Queen bed with memory-foam mattress and storage on both sides

  • Modern kitchen with 12V refrigerator, 2-burner cooktop, and convection microwave

  • TRUMA Combi furnace/water heater for efficient climate control

  • Lithium battery, solar prep, and electric jacks for easy setup

 

Whether you’re exploring off-grid or cruising cross-country, the Soaring Eagle AERIE 8 delivers premium comfort, smart design, and dependable performance in a compact, adventure-ready package.

There is also a rugged, durable composite interior wall board and LED interior light rings integrated into the vents to provide light in the evenings. Soaring Eagle OV-X truck topper camper Model 8.0 highlights:

  • Under-Bed Storage
  • LED Lights
  • Durable Construction
  • Quality Exterior Window

 

This is the perfect truck topper camper for an 8' bed! After you have been driving all day, you can find a campground to rest at for the night. The strut-assisted roof top features a water-resistant tent with integrated windows and screens and will provide more interior space to relax on the 78" x 74" bed. There is also convenient under-bed storage here for your belongings and camp gear. In the morning you can use the camp's shower to freshen up before using the optional portable Blackstone griddle to make breakfast, then head out for the day to hike, fish, or hunt!

 

The OV-X truck topper camper by Soaring Eagle is perfect for those who want simple, but comfortable camping options. The tubular aluminum construction includes fully insulated floor, sidewalls, endwalls and roof, and the quality exterior windows on each sidewall will provide ventilation while you're sleeping for the night. There is also a rugged, durable composite interior wall board and LED interior light rings integrated into the vents to provide light in the evenings. You may want to add one or more of the available options to further customize your camper, such as a MaxxAir Fan, a 200W or 400W solar panel roof system, rear flood lights, and more!

units.description: New 2026 Soaring Eagle AERIE 8
units.details:
Soaring Eagle AERIE truck camper 8 highlights:

  • Residential Queen-Size Bed
  • Two Burner Cooktop
  • Dual Bedside Nightstands
  • Wet Bath
  • 100Ah Lithium Battery
  • Maxxair Fans

 

Make each journey count with this cozy truck camper! Once you stop for the day, you can make dinner on the two-burner cooktop, grab a cold drink from the 12V refrigerator, and dine at the L-shaped dinette seating. There is a sink that will allow you to clean up the dishes while your camping companion sets up a board game! The wet bath on board means you won't have to leave the camper to wash up before bed, and speaking of bed, the residential quality mattress up front is sure to bring lots of comfort! There are also bedside storage compartments and nightstands, plus an additional wardrobe to keep your clothes wrinkle-free. 

 

The AERIE truck camper by Soaring Eagle is engineered and constructed to stand the test of time with its welded, tubular aluminum and composites and no wood throughout! This truck camper is designed for 3/4 ton and one-ton trucks and can fit an 8' bed with the tailgate closed. This allows you to use your own rear-view camera/sensors plus built-in steps that your truck may have. You'll also appreciate the fully enclosed and heated basement design for the best installation in its class, electric jacks for easy set-up, and a 20 lb. LP tank with a gauge. The interior of the AERIE will have you feeling right at home with its open floorplan, spacious bath, functional kitchen, and generous storage spaces!

units.description: New 2026 Soaring Eagle ADLAR 6.5XLS
units.details:
Soaring Eagle ADLAR truck camper 6.5XLS highlights:

  • 45" x 80" Bunk
  • Wardrobe
  • Electric Cooktop
  • Designed for Half-Ton Trucks

 

You can explore in complete comfort with this truck camper on your back! There is a comfortable 45" x 80" bunk up front to sleep on, or you can choose the optional 80" x 81" pull-out North/South bed. A two person dinette with a bench seat and fold-away table provides a place to enjoy your meal after it's been prepared on the two burner electric cooktop. There is also a 12V refrigerator that comes standard and an optional microwave oven if you want meals on the go. The portable cooktop can also be taken outside for added convenience, and the dinette can be converted for additional sleeping space for a guest. You can even add an optional commode to make camping trips that much easier!

 

Each one of these Soaring Eagle ADLAR truck campers take the concept of entry level campers and adds real functionality to it! Their entire construction consists of an all aluminum tubular construction for better strength, lighter weight, and indifference to water. The smooth fiberglass exterior and rugged black diamond pate aluminum skin around the lower perimeter will turn heads in the highway. There are LED exterior marker/clearance lights and LED exterior security light over the entrance door for you to see clearly at night. Come find your favorite one today!

units.description: New 2025 Bontrager Outdoors Compact 12ROK
units.details:
Bontrager Outdoors Compact teardrop trailer 12ROK highlights:

  • Outside Shower
  • Exterior Kitchenette
  • Overhead Cabinets
  • Fireplace
  • Under-Bed Storage

 

Pack your bags and head for the hills in this easy-to-tow trailer for two! The full outside kitchen includes everything you need to prepare meals each day, and there is an outside shower to fill the dogs water bowl or wash off your hiking boots. Head inside to rest on the mattress with storage below, or maybe just relax by the fireplace! This model also includes a countertop with storage below, an A/C and furnace to camp all year long, and a vent to keep fresh air moving inside. 

 

You can forge your own path with any one of these Bontrager Outdoors Compact teardrop trailers! You will find that each feature a welded aluminum frame construction and heavy-gauge, powder-coated aluminum wheel fenders. The side-entry doorway and Keyed Alike doors make it easy to enter, and the 30-AMP converter includes a detachable, easy-store power cord to keep you powered up. Each model includes an easy-plug solar prep package for the option to go off-grid, a portable toilet for hassle-free camping, a propane/CO detector, and 4-inch, deluxe comfort, quilted bed mattresses to ensure a great night's rest wherever you roam.
